<sect1 id="dir_4204bade821bb161f94e043d2260f465_1autotoc_md112">
<title>helios::engine::core::units</title><para>Canonical unit definitions for consistent spatial and temporal measurements.</para>
<para>This module provides standardized units and conversion helpers to keep spatial and temporal data consistent across all helios modules. Using consistent units prevents scaling errors and simplifies physics calculations.</para>
</sect1>
